{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AJ81bDtWLEp4ZWY3KhZ1TG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n     2→\n     3→### Session 34 — state corruption fix #18, no-op (2026-03-27T15:48Z)\n     4→\n     5→- **State corruption fix #18**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 at `review` in sprint-state.json, epic-16 at `backlog`. All 4 stories confirmed done via `git log` (commits with \"verified and done\") and proof documents exist in `verification/`.\n     6→- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70→74), set epic-16 to `done` in sprint-status.yaml.\n     7→- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph process with stale in-memory state continues to overwrite. This has been the same issue since session 31+. The fix deployed in session 22 (`registerStory` guard) prevents new phantoms but doesn't prevent ralph from reverting statuses of existing stories.\n     8→- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n     9→\n    10→## Token Report\n    11→- Total tool calls: ~12\n    12→- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 3, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Grep: 0\n    13→- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n    14→- Redundant operations: None — efficient diagnosis of known recurring issue\n    15→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"177033ae-c202-4c71-8c11-01800891f3a8","uuid":"f763b847-a57a-4327-be6f-ee4cd5a6c8ea","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:51:22.985Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-27\n\n### Session 34 — state corruption fix #18, no-op (2026-03-27T15:48Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #18**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 at `review` in sprint-state.json, epic-16 at `backlog`. All 4 stories confirmed done via `git log` (commits with \"verified and done\") and proof documents exist in `verification/`.\n- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70→74), set epic-16 to `done` in sprint-status.yaml.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph process with stale in-memory state continues to overwrite. This has been the same issue since session 31+. The fix deployed in session 22 (`registerStory` guard) prevents new phantoms but doesn't prevent ralph from reverting statuses of existing stories.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~12\n- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 3, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Grep: 0\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — efficient diagnosis of known recurring issue\n","numLines":15,"startLine":1,"totalLines":15}}}
